""SELECT f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\" AS \"ProvinceName\", (
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM (
        SELECT DISTINCT t4.\"FarmId\"
        FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t3 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t3.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f0 ON t3.\"FarmId\" = f0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p0 ON f0.\"ProvinceId\" = p0.\"Id\"
        INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t4 ON t1.\"TillageProgramId\" = t4.\"Id\"
        WHERE NOT (t1.\"Deleted\") AND t3.\"IsActive\" AND f.\"ProvinceId\" = f0.\"ProvinceId\" AND p.\"Name\" = p0.\"Name\"
    ) AS t2) AS \"FarmCount\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) AS \"TotalHectares\", COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) AS \"CompletedHectares\", COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\", CASE
    WHEN COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\") FILTER (WHERE t.\"IsCompleted\"), 0) / COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0)) * 100
    ELSE 0
END AS \"CompletionPercentage\"
FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t
INNER JOIN \"TillagePrograms\" AS t0 ON t.\"TillageProgramId\" = t0.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Farms\" AS f ON t0.\"FarmId\" = f.\"Id\"
INNER JOIN \"Provinces\" AS p ON f.\"ProvinceId\" = p.\"Id\"
WHERE NOT (t.\"Deleted\") AND t0.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY f.\"ProvinceId\", p.\"Name\"
ORDER BY COALESCE(sum(t.\"Hectares\"), 0) DESC"

    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t1
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t1.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0)::int AS \"TotalServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT count(*)::int
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t2
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t2.\"TillageProgramId\" AND t2.\"IsCompleted\")), 0)::int AS \"CompletedServices\", COALESCE(sum((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(COALESCE(t3.\"ServiceCost\", 0.0)), 0.0)
    FROM \"TillageServices\" AS t3
    WHERE t.\"Id\" = t3.\"TillageProgramId\")), 0.0) AS \"TotalRevenue\"
FROM \"TillagePrograms\" AS t
WHERE t.\"FarmId\" = @__farmId_0 AND t.\"IsActive\"
GROUP BY t.\"FarmId\"
LIMIT 1"
